- Workers: Warehouse management > Setup > Worker

PACKING:
- Packing profiles: Warehouse management > Setup > Packing > Packing profiles
- Packing station: Warehouse management > Setup > Packing > Packing station setup
- Container types: Warehouse management > Setup > Containers > Container types

